arStrings.szText: The Way Out is Through
Travel through the Tangles to Samuk
Travel through the Tangles to Samuk

With the council's permission to pass the western gate of Lower Kurast, I will cut my way through the Tangles and reach Samuk with Neyrelle. There we will find the Tomb of Akarat where the connection between Neyrelle and the soulstone can be safely severed before she succumbs to its dark power.
